sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Gateway as "Gateway" <<boundary>>
    participant Controller as "Controller" <<control>>
    participant Domain as "Domain" <<entity>>
    participant Database as "Database" <<database>>
    participant Cache as "Cache" <<collections>>
    participant Queue as "Queue" <<queue>>
    User ->> Gateway: HTTP request
    Gateway ->> Controller: Route
    Controller ->> Domain: Process
    Domain ->> Database: Query
    Domain ->> Cache: Check
    Domain ->> Queue: Publish
